lank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/S%C6%A1n-c%C6%B0-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-046/poem-79Lqs3uJwEPDrpmJJPDLnQ">Sơn cư bách vịnh kỳ 046 - 山居百詠其四十六</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-jnvtlp5PrNS3FoOBBGt7-w">Tông Bản thiền sư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/T%E1%BA%B7ng-Ngh%C4%A9a-Xuy%C3%AAn-c%C3%B4ng-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-F8uGH1O_0wkt7RZ1vQ_QSQ">Tặng Nghĩa Xuyên công kỳ 1 - 贈義川公其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/author-kBTBt5Mbi6PPrH2sJkQAPw">Khuyết danh Việt Nam</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B9ng-Duy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BB%B7/Th%C3%A1i-tang-t%E1%BB%AD-k%E1%BB%B3-18/poem-A7VPbBTNYJ4wI3UA3_t7zw">Thái tang tử kỳ 18 - 采桑子其十八</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B9ng-Duy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BB%B7/author-NkGwR6r3M3j5cQXaNNhfvQ">Phùng Duyên Kỷ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-b%E1%BB%87nh-kh%E1%BB%9Fi-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-BYfga5xn8kIzUu5uu0DHLw">Xuân nhật bệnh khởi kỳ 1 - 春日病起其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/author-FSJg5-ivZkPUR1nhJkA6Fg">Lê Thánh Tông</a>)<br></div>	</div>
